Class LonelyProcessingStep

  • java.lang.Object

    DeleteDuplicateNodesStep, IdMapperPreparationStep
    public abstract class LonelyProcessingStep
extends AbstractStep<Void>
    Step that doesn't receive batches, doesn't send batches downstream; just processes data.

      • receive

        public long receive​(long ticket,
                    Void nothing)
        Description copied from interface: Step
        Receives a batch from upstream, queues it for processing.
        Parameters:
        ticket - ticket associates with the batch. Tickets are generated by producing steps and must follow each batch all the way through a stage.
        nothing - the batch object to queue for processing.
        Returns:
        how long it time (millis) was spent waiting for a spot in the queue.
